)</span></td>\n   <td>34.0 (34)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>ECDH</code></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/41\" title=\"Released on 2015-09-22.\">41</a> (41)</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"veja_também","title":"Veja também","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Crypto\"><code>Crypto</code></a> e <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Crypto/subtle\"><code>Crypto.subtle</code></a>.</li>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/SubtleCrypto\"><code>SubtleCrypto</code></a>, a interface a qual ele pertence.</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"dicionário","title":"Dicionário:","isH3":true,"content":"<p>\"Key\" = \"Chave\"</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Sintaxe","id":"sintaxe"},{"text":"Especificações","id":"especificações"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"Veja também","id":"veja_também"}],"summary":"O método SubtleCrypto.importKey() retorna como Promise de uma CryptoKey de uma informção dada como parâmetro.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"SubtleCrypto.importKey()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/api/subtlecrypto/importkey","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/api/subtlecrypto/importkey/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API","title":"APIs da Web"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/SubtleCrypto","title":"SubtleCrypto"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/SubtleCrypto/importKey","title":"SubtleCrypto.importKey()"}],"pageTitle":"SubtleCrypto.importKey() - APIs da Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}